  ('medical-tech-moex-11898', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-102-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者無法使鏈球菌之streptolysin O在sheep blood agar（BAP）上發揮明顯的溶血作用？', '["在BAP表面接種後，放厭氧環境培養", "將菌與blood agar混合後倒入平板（Pour plate），凝固後放CO 培養箱 2", "在BAP表面接種後，再於表面劃線接種S. aureus ATCC 25923菌株", "在BAP表面接種後，穿刺數下，放CO 培養箱 2"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0770013e9b2e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a3e37902d519", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102100", "c": "311", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技牙醫師分試藥師醫事檢驗師醫放師助產師物理治療師職能治療師呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
